NUMBER 288
NAME Poor Quarter
*DESCRIPTION_START
You walk within the eerie shadow of the empty buildings, all empty, that
is, save one partially restored warehouse. A pile of shattered crates has
been cleared from the center of the street and from around the door of
the warehouse and the sign mounted on the wall beside it.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT NW 284
EXIT E 289

EXIT ABOVE 2152

ITEM 0 943 VAL2=1861 VAL1=100 UNLOCKED CLOSED VAL3=1861
ITEM 1 204 ADJ1=355
EXTEND 1 on the wall of a warehouse
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Poor Quarter Reclamation Society.
Please come in!
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
Poor Quarter Reclamation Society.
*DESCRIPTION_END


NUMBER 1861
NAME Entry Hall

INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

*DESCRIPTION_START
This utilitarian hallway leads into the center of the building. On the
east wall is a pine door while on the south end of the hall is an oaken
door. An archway leads west and an exit leads out to the street at the
north end of the hallway. An opening leads to another corridor south of,
and parallel to the one going to the daycare center.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 288
