NUMBER 1863
NAME Multifunction Room

INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

*DESCRIPTION_START
Designed for many uses this large, open room serves as a community center
most of the time with crafts and skills taught. In rarer cases, however,
tables are rearranged for dinner events or hung up on the wall for audience
events. Closed serving windows on the west wall give access to the
kitchen. A plaque is on the west wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 65 ADJ1=216 VAL1=10 UNLOCKED VAL3=1861 VAL2=1861
ITEM 1 400
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
This building is a solid tribute to the kindness of certain citizens of
Fayd towards their less fortunate brethren. This is but the first step
towards making Fayd an enjoyable place to live for all citizens. If you
would like to make a donation, please place any quantity of gold, silver
or copper coins on the ground and point to it. Any amount will be greatly
appreciated!
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
        IFPREVERB PLUGH -1
                CLEARVERB
                NEWPUT 4 546
                NEWPUT 5 1387 VAL2=4
                NEWPUT 6 790 ADJ1=54 ADJ2=718
                NEWPUT 7 1520 ADJ1=298
                NEWPUT 8 573 ADJ1=54
        ENDIF
ENDIF

ITEM 4 91

ITEM 5 448 ADJ1=192 OPEN
ITEM 6 448 ADJ2=587 OPEN
ITEM 7 448 ADJ1=29 OPEN
ITEM 8 448 ADJ1=259 OPEN


IFPREVERB POINT -1
        IFVAR ARCHNUM = 163
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER A woman takes the donation, bowing her thanks to you quickly.
                ECHO OTHERS A woman takes %n's donation, bowing her thanks.
                ADD PQCOPPER ITEMVAL1
                REMOVEITEM -1
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ARCHNUM = 162
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER A woman takes the donation, bowing her thanks to you.
                ECHO OTHERS A woman takes %n's donation, bowing her thanks.
                ADD PQSILVER ITEMVAL1
                REMOVEITEM -1
        ENDIF
        IFVAR ARCHNUM = 161
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO PLAYER A woman takes the donation, bowing her profuse thanks to you.
                ECHO OTHERS A woman takes %n's donation, bowing her profuse thanks.
                ADD PQGOLD ITEMVAL1
                REMOVEITEM -1
        ENDIF
        IFVAR PQCOPPER > 10
                EQUAL DUMMY1 PQCOPPER
                DIV DUMMY1 10
                ADD PQSILVER DUMMY1
                MOD PQCOPPER 10
        ENDIF
        IFVAR PQSILVER > 10
                EQUAL DUMMY1 PQSILVER
                DIV DUMMY1 10
                ADD PQGOLD DUMMY1
                MOD PQSILVER 10
        ENDIF
        IFVAR PQGOLD > 0
                ADD PVAL15 PQGOLD
                EQUAL PQGOLD 0
        ENDIF
        IFVAR PVAL15 > 25000
                SUB PVAL15 25000
                ADD PVAL16 25
        ENDIF
ENDIF


