NUMBER 1870
NAME Warehouse
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is the remainder of the warehouse that isn't furnished, but it isn't
being wasted. A number of frames for structures are on the wall, assembled
here before hauled out and put together. Experienced carpenters train
willing neighborhood apprentices. Large quantities of supplies are stacked
in here in crates and on shelves.
*DESCRIPTION_END

